==English==
===Noun===
'''[[Komodo]] [[dragon]]''' (Komodo dragons)

# An [[endangered species]] of [[monitor lizard]] native to certain [[Indonesian]] islands [[east]] of [[Java]].  It is the world's [[largest]] [[lizard]], growing to 10 [[feet]] or 3 [[meter]]s.  It is known for its ability to kill [[prey]] with its [[septic]] [[saliva]]; the resulting [[septicemia]] can kill so quickly that it was once [[suspect]]ed the lizard was [[venomous]].

====Scientific names====
*[[Varanus comodoensis]]

====Synonyms====
*[[dragon lizard]]
*[[giant lizard]]
*[[Komodo lizard]]

